summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed to the Public executed on July 29, 1907, by the Realty Loan and Banking Company, a corporation, trustee, Fred J. C. Miller and Gunhild K. Miller, his wife, and N. B. Frisbie, for a part of tracts 28, 29, 31, 32 and 33, Kelsey's Brighton Beach Five Acre Tracts.
